data.meta_description: Salomea OF BERG was born about 1097, daughter of Henry I OF BERG and Adelaide OF MOCHENTAL. She was married in the year 1115 to Boleslaw III Wrymouth OF POLAND, they had 5 children. She died on July 27, 1144 in Leczyca, Poland. This information is part of Family tree Riny Doyle geboren Marinus van Waard by Riny Doyle on Genealogy Online.
